{"tid":443282,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［震驚］塞爾維亞市長訪台食一口麵包即死亡","createTime":"2017-10-21T12:55:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-22T06:42:30.000Z","uid":41351,"like":195,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"f53de9acb57a982dffb4290eedf9a576f9a15684","tid":443282,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T12:55:40.000Z","msg":"一名塞爾維亞市長訪問台灣期間，中午在宜蘭餐廳吃飯時，突然昏倒並失去生命跡象，送往醫院搶救後不治，警方現正調查意外原因。<br />\n<br />\n來自塞爾維亞克盧賽瓦奇市的市長Dragi Nestorovic，與塞爾維亞地方經濟發展聯盟執行長及其他五位市長，一同受邀到台灣出席慶祝中華民國成立慶典。中午他在宜蘭一間餐廳吃飯時，只是剛吃一口麵包就突然昏迷，隨後臉色發紫並失去生命跡象，送往陽明大學附設醫院急救後，最終證實不治。<br />\n<br />\n救護人員表示，懷疑他是被麵包噎到所致，但送往醫院後確認不是噎到，實際死因有待調查。而台方外交部人員已接手處理事件，拒絕評論事件。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/chi/1044545/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fchi%2F1044545%2F&d=HFPyR1jp%2FGpiZBTBZvAxqE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=eb1c3d7e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fchi%2F1044545%2F&h=a0a852de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/chi/1044545/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/21/205512_438e37e967bb4ef9dbbc9abad748a032.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F21%2F205512_438e37e967bb4ef9dbbc9abad748a032.jpg&h=456d9a61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢單野好可疑"},{"pid":"8cf8a33855a53f26439ea4670064dc659ab5aecf","tid":443282,"uid":139687,"like":177,"dislike":15,"score":162,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T12:57:45.000Z","msg":"台灣D野食有齊曬成個periodic table D elements <br />\n食死人有幾奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6024bd8c9134e37f10f2f5ebe2ad77e3cda0b262","tid":443282,"uid":76216,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T12:58:23.000Z","msg":"暗殺"},{"pid":"ea01277b026ebb6d7ac378a80fc1951a162978cb","tid":443282,"uid":55488,"like":42,"dislike":7,"sco